\begin_layout Standard
Once you reach level 25 you will be allowed to build the Fortress building.
 It's the main one in the Fortress screen and determines the wood and stone
 capacity of your storage.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The level of the Fortress building also determines the amount of wood and
 stone rewards you get from wheel of fortune, dice or quests during the
 Fortress event.
\end_layout

