\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Do quests to reach level 18.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Buy new equipment.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Defeat 1-2 more dungeons.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Improve album again.
 By that time you should have at least 35% of album, but +40% is highly
 recommended.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
If you have lots of time on your hands, try to get the achievement for 3
