 That gives you only +5 stats on everything, but if you use the `/gold bet
 1` command in the chat box, it doesn't cost much gold.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Do quests to reach level 20
\series default
 and to find the 
\series bold
key for the second dungeon
\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Try both dungeons again.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
If you are very close to completing a level, do 1-2 quests to close the
 level, before changing items.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Change all items with better.
 At level 20 you can find items with +40 total stats.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Improve album.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Next goal is to reach level 25 at reset time.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Try dungeons again.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
If you are blocked and want to reach more than level 25 in the first day,
