\begin_layout Enumerate
At some point you might find out that changing epics is just not enough
 to continue, even if you have the best ones.
 If that happens, the reason could be that you neglected your base stats.
 So, remember to also use some of your gold to upgrade the stats.
 You can check how much you need, by looking at other players with a similar
 level to yours.
 You could also use the dungeon simulator, adding arbitrary points to your
 base stats, until the chances of defeating the dungeon become at least
 1%.
\end_layout

